{"tid":2433634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：民陣涉違反《國安法　》 短時間內或遭取締","createTime":"2021-03-05T04:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T06:22:49.000Z","uid":227801,"like":11,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"deb1a690d7911f3c697ec7ab780391b42244c218","tid":2433634,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:19:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E6%97%A9%E5%A0%B1-%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E6%AD%A3%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E9%81%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E7%9F%AD%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E5%85%A7%E6%88%96%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%96%E7%B7%A0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%259F%25AD%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%258F%2596%25E7%25B7%25A0%2F&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=882af194\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%259F%25AD%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%258F%2596%25E7%25B7%25A0%2F&h=fff6625c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E6%97%A9%E5%A0%B1-%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E6%AD%A3%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E9%81%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E7%9F%AD%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E5%85%A7%E6%88%96%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%96%E7%B7%A0/</a><br />\n新加坡《聯合早報》今日引述不具名消息指，香港當局正調查民間人權陣線（民陣）是否違反《港區國安法》，民陣在短時間內有可能會被特區政府取締。報道指，調查有關民陣是否接受美國國家民主基金會資助舉辦反修例運動，一旦證實屬實，民陣可能因違反《國安法》而被取締。<br />\n《聯合早報》引述不具名消息人士指，早前網上流傳民陣曾接受美國國家民主基金會（National Endowment for Democracy，簡稱 NED）資助舉辦反修例活動，當局正進行調查，一旦證實屬實，民陣將違反《香港國安法》，或被政府取締。不過報道未有提及消息來源，也未提及調查由什麼部門進行。<br />\n報道又引述不具名消息指，民陣一直沒有向政府註冊，有可能觸犯《社團條例》。一旦罪成，民陣負責人最高可被監禁三個月。<br />\n<br />\n《大公報》2019 年曾發表時評，指民陣多次發起遊行，「每次遊行都構成了嚴重社會動盪」，對香港公共安全、國家安全構成嚴重破壞；時評又指，民陣與外國政治組織勾結，「鐵證如山」，促請特區政府取締民陣。"},{"pid":"e9741674b5e5d2fefca5d25639222fe6b09431d7","tid":2433634,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8368594d84aad192ab6a4335aba74aee0c3238d1","tid":2433634,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9636621b0df373c344fe341dae6c0175df106a","tid":2433634,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e495968927bd938747ecfe4b9bc1632970e6f07","tid":2433634,"uid":19485,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:27:53.000Z","msg":"又係過去犯未來法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc626b28b8084aa80ab3a19cf37c127565d9f37f","tid":2433634,"uid":238828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:28:55.000Z","msg":"龍門任你擺~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21878946d437b06fe9037cb1bc4084435339a02b","tid":2433634,"uid":145273,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":